nuclear destruction 
turners better world society founded in 1985 is sponsoring a 
series of television programs on such subjects as overpopulation 
and nuclear proliferation and the most recent is the terror 
trade buying the bomb airing tonight and again saturday on 
superstation tbs 
the content of the onehour documentary is impressive not to 
mention scary 
the centerpiece is an interview with eric a man who claims 
to be a former arms dealer who traded in blackmarket plutonium 
sought by many third world nations as well as terrorist 
organizations wanting to build their own nuclear weapons 
