for accuracy only an unusual run of invalid signatures could block 
the drive doty said i dont think were going to find that im 
not seeing that now 
while there is some dispute about procedures denvers charter 
calls for an entirely new election 
any candidate who collected 300 names on a nominating petition 
could run and if no candidate mustered a clear majority a runoff 
