doug jewett seattle city attorney said the city would pay 68 
million while its insurance carriers would pay 438 million 
we think it is a good settlement for the city because the 
dollar amount is less than would have been spent on defense 
costs alone those costs have been running 25 million a year 
jewett said 
of even more concern to the city of seattle was its risk as 
