pages to the front page agreed that newspaper management has to 
make a fullscale commitment to hiring and promoting women and 
minorities 
people tend to hire people like themselves mills said 
its a clone factor affirmative action at least reduces that 
clone factor but its a commitment at the top that brings 
change she said 
